Non-contact payment:
:SKRSLUT.
.br
By using the non-contact payment solution you pay by means of the chip of
the card without inserting the card in the card terminal. You just have to
hold the card in a distance of 0-3 cm from the non-contact symbol on the
terminal when paying.
